nodes.text: Building 9819 was a building that was located in the city Oluna Biqua, on the planet Genarius.

During the time of the Clone Wars, members of the Metatheran Cartel offloaded a canister of the gas Trinex-M at Building 9819. However, following an outbreak of the gas, a Z-95 Headhunter crashed into the building and destroyed it. Shortly afterwards, the Heroes of Cularin encountered the information broker Morth next to the building's remains.
